{"word":"G2828 - κλισία - klisía - klee-see'-ah - Company","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κλισία</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">klisía</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">klee-see'-ah</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Company</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Noun Feminine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (பெண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"பந்தி - பெண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"1. a hut"},{"paragraph":"2. a tent"},{"paragraph":"3. a chair"},{"paragraph":"4. a company reclining; a row or party of persons reclining at meal"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a derivative of <a href=\"#/G2827 - κλίνω - klínō - klee'-no/2827\">G2827</a>; properly <i>reclination</i>, that is, (concretely and specifically) a <i>party</i> at a meal: - company.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}